		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=354833"><span id=Scholar>neverdone</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />92 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.39]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=neverdone&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>For the Bandolier, press the 'b' key.&nbsp;&nbsp;To use it, select 'Add'; it will set your current weapons as one of four possible sets.  Name it, and make a hot key.  Set up another one, and another hot key.<br><br>I find this a fantastic option! I used to be really fast switching weapons, and known for it, but this really kicks!  Made a big difference to my fighting.<br><br>Journey far and fare well!<br></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Journey far and fare well!</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
